OL,3,CEgyptian pyramid to be clad in granite
OL,4,Cblocks - but not everyone is impressed
OL,6,FAt almost 5,000 years old the Pyramid
OL,7,Fof Menkaure is looking rather good for
OL,8,Fits age. But to the horror of
OL,9,Farcheologists it is being restored as
OL,10,Fbuilders intended, Geraint Vincent
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FAn Egyptian pyramid is being clad in
OL,14,Fgranite blocks in a renovation
OL,15,Fprogramme dubbed as the "project of
OL,16,Fthe century" by local archaeologists -
OL,17,Fbut not everybody approves of the
OL,18,Fchanges.
