OL,3,CEgyptian pyramid to be clad in granite
OL,4,Cblocks - but not everyone is impressed
OL,6,FThe Pyramid of Menkaure, the smallest
OL,7,Fof the three pyramids in Giza, will be
OL,8,Frestored in a way that will allow
OL,9,Ftourists to see the site how it would
OL,10,Fhave appeared in ancient times, the
OL,11,FSecretary General of the Supreme
OL,12,FCouncil of Antiquities in Egypt, Dr
OL,13,FMostafa Waziri said, speaking in front
OL,14,Fof the pyramid on Friday.
OL,16,FThe project involves excavating the
OL,17,Farea around the pyramid, and then work
OL,18,Fto match the fallen granite stones
OL,19,Fwith the stones in the pyramid will
OL,20,Fcommence.
