OL,3,CEgyptian pyramid to be clad in granite
OL,4,Cblocks - but not everyone is impressed
OL,6,F"We do not know the date on which the
OL,7,Fgranite stones that covered the
OL,8,FPyramid of Menkaure fell, but the time
OL,9,Fhas come to return them as they were
OL,10,Fin ancient Egypt, through the Century
OL,11,FProject, in cooperation with the
OL,12,FJapanese mission in Cairo," Dr Waziri
OL,13,Fsaid, as reported by Al Arabiya.
OL,15,FBut one online commentator said
OL,16,Faltering the ancient monument makes a
OL,17,F"Disneyland from ancient legacy".
