OL,3,CEgyptian pyramid to be clad in granite
OL,4,Cblocks - but not everyone is impressed
OL,6,FA local historian likened the project
OL,7,Fto a puzzle game, where each stone of
OL,8,Fthe pyramid needs to be matched up
OL,9,Fwith a falling granite block.
OL,11,F"It is not an easy task," Dr. Bassam
OL,12,FAl-Shamaa local media.
OL,14,FBut the vast undertaking has been
OL,15,Fcriticised by some who think it is
OL,16,Fbest to leave the pyramid in its
OL,17,Foriginal state, without the additional
OL,18,Fstone.
