OL,3,CEgyptian pyramid to be clad in granite
OL,4,Cblocks - but not everyone is impressed
OL,6,F"It is destroying an ancient monument,
OL,7,Flegacy for all humanity, not only the
OL,8,Ftoday's country of Egypt. Please
OL,9,Frespect the past, do not make
OL,10,FDisneyland from ancient legacy. These
OL,11,Fmonuments not only for people who want
OL,12,Fto make nice selfie photo," one man
OL,13,Fwrote on Facebook.
OL,15,F"Oh what a shame, it will turn into a
OL,16,Fmodern one as well will loose part of
OL,17,Fits historical grandeur," one user
OL,18,Fcommented beneath a video of the
OL,19,Frestoration work.
